Global Portable Air Purifiers Market Insights
Portable Air Purifiers Market Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 8.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 11.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Portable Air Purifiers Market Overview
The global Portable Air Purifiers market was valued at USD 10.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 18.3 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.4% during the forecast period. The rise in air pollution levels, coupled with an increasing focus on health and wellness, is driving the demand for portable air purifiers. The market is segmented into various types, including HEPA filters, carbon filters, and UV filters, with the HEPA filter segment dominating the market share. Growth is particularly significant in North America, Europe, and Asia-Pacific due to the increasing awareness about air quality and the rising health concerns among consumers.

